{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Fully incorporate EU food safety standards into UK law",
        "additional_details": "We believe that the EU has some of the most robust food standards worldwide. Also this will help us in avoiding or minimising required paperwork when exporting food products from the UK to the EU and vice versa.",
        "background": "We are asking that the EU food safety standards in thier entirety are incorporated into UK law.",
